ign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Rangers can out dmg us!?</span><hr size=1> I hate to break it to you but rangers with Endless quiver, am3, good bow &amp; arrows, 1600+ atk can outdamage wizards in SHORT fights as well as long ones. Don't know why everything thinks a ranger needs a long fight to get mega damage. The top end rangers get 200 to 300 dps with trueshot which lasts 2 min and after that they still have great damage going for them. No wizard is gonna equal that and not get himself summoned into a pan cake. Even if you had garrison's AND for some reason you could chain cast it without getting summoned AND you didn't get any resists you could break 300 dps but you couldn't keep that up for 2 solid minutes without some serious mana feeding which means necros, mages, and a healer helping you.<br>
<br>
Personally i don't mind because 99.99% of the ranger population will never reach that level.<br>
